已知信息：
'A substance that has been shown by an extensive set of analytical tests to be authentic material that should be of high purity. This standard can be:—obtained from an officially recognized source;
—prepared by independent synthesis;
—obtained from existing production material of high purity; or
—prepared by further purification of existing production material.'可被翻译为：经大量分析试验证明为真实材料的物质，应具有高纯度。该标准可以是:-从官方认可的来源获得;
-独立合成制备;
-从现有的高纯度生产材料中获得;或
-通过进一步提纯现有生产材料制备。
'reference substance'可被翻译为：对照品

根据上述已知信息，请将'A high-purity non-standard substance provided by a pharmaceutical reference substance development institution.'翻译为中文，只能输出翻译后的句子，不允许添加编造成分。
